I. About
========

  The primesieve GUI application has been developed with the Qt
  framework (http://qt-project.org). This file explains how to install
  Qt and how to compile the primesieve GUI application.

II. How to build primesieve (All operating systems)
===================================================

  Requirement
  -----------
  The primesieve GUI application requires a compiler that supports
  OpenMP 3.0 or later (2008). The Qt SDK includes a recent version of
  g++ which works fine.

  1. For Windows download and install the latest Qt 4 SDK:
     ftp://ftp.trolltech.com/qt/source/qt-win-opensource-4.8.1-mingw.exe

     For all other OSes download and install the latest Qt 5 SDK:
     http://qt-project.org/downloads

  2. Launch the primesieve.pro project file with the Qt-Creator IDE
     and have a look at Qt-Creator-build-settings.png for the
     compilation steps.

     Alternatively you can also run the following commands from a
     terminal to directly build a primesieve binary:

     $ qmake; make
